text: The Cajundome is a 13,500-seat multi-purpose arena in Lafayette, Louisiana. The Louisiana Ragin' Cajuns men's and women's basketball programs play there. University events and commencement ceremonies including high school graduations also happen there. == References == Category:Lafayette, Louisiana Category:Buildings and structures in Louisiana Category:20th-century establishments in Louisiana Category:1985 establishments in the United States
title: Cajundome
